Uses of Class
CommonLib.messages.Message

  • Packages that use Message 
    Package Description
    ClientSide.client
    'client' package contains the application entry point, and some functionalities like configuration and connectivity.
    ClientSide.controllers
    'controllers' package contains the classes which has the UI logic.
    CommonLib.messages
    'message' package contains all the messages mechanism of the communication between the client and the server.
    ServerSide.connectivity
    'connectivity' package contains the classes that related to server configuration.
    ServerSide.db
    'db' package contains the classes that responsible on the communication with the database.
